						<summary>

						<p>On the north wall of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the central shrine in the Vēdāraṇyēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Kulōttuṅgachōḷa III. Year 32: 1210 A.D.</p>						

						<p>The details of date, <hi rend="italic">viz.</hi>, Dhanus, ba. 9, Monday, Chittirai corresponds to 1210 A.D., December 11. The week day was Saturday and not Monday.</p>						

						<p>This incomplete inscription stops with mentioning Kalyāṇapuraṅgoṇḍa-śōḻapaṭṭiṉam in Kāṉattūr-nāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
