<lb n="2" break="no"/>ttalaiyuṅkoṇṭu virāapi<hi rend="grantha">ṣe</hi>kamum vicaiyar Api<hi rend="grantha">ṣe</hi>kamum paṇṇiya<unclear>ru</unclear>ḷiṉa tiri
