<lb n="5" break="no"/>yāṇapuraṅkoṇṭacoḻapaṭṭiṉat<unclear>tu</unclear> nakarattukkuc camainta Uyyavan<unclear>tā</unclear>ṉ paḷḷi<note n="188-1">The record is incomplete.</note>
